{"tid":1597624,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[突發]港大學生會前會長孫曉嵐 涉逗留會議廳被落案","createTime":"2019-09-27T04:38:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T06:14:11.000Z","uid":68738,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e93bad004d008646b43a7b3e17d864c4520de0ad","tid":1597624,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T04:38:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190927/large/1569558704_75bc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190927%2Flarge%2F1569558704_75bc.jpg&h=d013e945&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港大學生會前會長孫曉嵐，上月29日被警方以涉嫌「串謀摧毀及損壞財產」與「進入或逗留會議廳範圍」拘捕。今早她在fb上貼文，指已被落案起訴。<br />\n<br />\n孫曉嵐在fb貼文說：「今日到警署報到，警方正式落案起訴我「進入或逗留在會議廳範圍，將於30/9（下星期一）下午二時於東區法院一號法庭提堂。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190927/60089940\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190927%2F60089940&d=6kTjEm0JFzAR16ySTE8tYvYtrFBHe52Fn%2F6n3rMGN5k%3D&h=e0c0f4c8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190927%2F60089940&h=9e683d1a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190927/60089940</a>"},{"pid":"0dc5b3b86e267dd1f9a945bfa5ed29cf06cfe0bb","tid":1597624,"uid":169079,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T04:39:17.000Z","msg":"重對話？清算已經開始"},{"pid":"796e32bd247295618c50b7390ff09b490f1ddf55","tid":1597624,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T04:44:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"421759f77e847e316922772af8e8ed8e7c551fb5","tid":1597624,"uid":31389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T04:49:18.000Z","msg":"鳩拉"},{"pid":"1df134e85c5193f93f94df3673aae0b94edf80e6","tid":159762